   ISRAEL-U.N. (United Nations) _ Israel has accepted an invitation
to join the U.N. regional group, giving it the chance for the first
time to be part of U.N. bodies like the Security Council. By
Barbara Crossette.
</P>
<P>
   UNICEF-DOMESTIC-VIOLENCE (United Nations) _ Unicef, continuing
its expansion of areas of concern, has issued a report on domestic
violence around the world. By Barbara Crossette.
</P>
<P>
   AFRICA-WORLDBANK (Washington) _ Civil war and disease have made
sub-Saharan Africa worse off than it has been since 1960, the World
Bank said in a new study of the region. By Joseph Kahn.
