   PSORIASIS-BIOTECH (Undated) _ The biotechnology industry is
taking aim at psoriasis, a chronic disease that affects an
estimated 7 million Americans and, in its more serious forms, is
far more physically and psychologically devastating than it is
often thought to be. By Andrew Pollack.
