image-defining underwear and jeans brands. It is a bitterly
personal suit has many fashion industry insiders wondering whether
the aging designer is looking to avenge himself on Warnco's
tough-as-flint chief executive Linda J. Wachner. By Leslie Kaufman.
</P>
<P>
