r l BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV04-C     06-01 0590
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV04-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: CAUGHT IN A LOVE NET
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (l) lifestyle categories for
release Sunday, June 4.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
