<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-01 11:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1687 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-CPT-ECOMMERCE-COLUMN-     06-01 1371
