<P>
   ELECTRICITY-SHORTAGES (Washington) _ Energy experts warn that
consumers, with their stepped-up use of air conditioners, likely
will see months of power brownout and blackout alerts this summer.
Areas most at risk are New York, New England, and the Southwest,
including California. By MARK HELM.
</P>
<P>
   CONLEY-SPELLING _ Sean Conley, a slender 12-year-old from
Newark, Calif., confidently cruises through two more rounds of
increasingly tougher words on the final day of the 73rd National
Spelling Bee. He correctly spells Mackinaw and ferriferous. By JUDY
HOLLAND. (1stLd-Writethru will be filed to story that moved earlier
today.)
</P>
<P>
