</P>
<P>
   SCI-STROKE-RECOVER (Undated) _ Researchers have confirmed that
even in older stroke victims, the brain can overcome some damage
caused by strokes. By Sandra Blakeslee.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-SKIN-CANCER (Denver) _ Researchers are using gene therapy to
treat skin cancer. By Sheryl Gay Stolberg.
</P>
