<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-01 15:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1900 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l BC-CARS-REVIEW-ART-BOS &LR;      06-01 0855
