   FOOTBALL
</P>
<P>
   LEWIS-TRIAL _ ATLANTA _ Prosecution continues its case today in
the case against Baltimore Ravens' All-Pro linebacker Ray Lewis.
Lewis' statement may go before the jury today in his murder trial.
(Rankin/Torpy, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Moving in (a) General News and (s) Sports categories.
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
