<HEADLINE>
WARDING OFF COMPUTER COOTIES
</HEADLINE>
  (Eds: A copy of this is also being transmitted to entertainment
wire) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By DAVID BLOOM 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The recent pair of computer virus scares sparked a few thoughts,
particularly as I plowed into the massive paperback version of
