<P>
   BUSH-DNA (Austin, Texas) _ We look at how many other death-row
inmates in Texas might seek the same consideration that Gov. George
W. Bush is giving a convicted rapist-murderer, who has won a 30-day
reprieve so that he can continue to pursue an appeal of his
sentence. By JOHN GONZALEZ.
