strain on Prime Minister Ehud Barak's unwieldy governing coalition.
</P>
<P>
   ``This bill is fundamentalist in its essence and truly
frightening,'' said Naomi Chazan, a parliamentarian from the
liberal Meretz party, which is part of the governing coalition.
</P>
<P>
   ``We will do everything to prevent Israel from turning into an
